  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ExperimentCaseInfo
    Interface every concrete experiment case must implement, comprising all methods that allow to get experiment case information
    ExperimentInfo
    Interface every concrete experiment must implement, comprising all methods that allow to get experiment information
    UniqueIdentifier
    Interface implemented by classes which guarantee they provide a way to uniquely identify an instance based on some value
    Versionable
    Interface implemented by classes which are able to provide a version number used to distinguish updated instances
